abstract: American Austin Ernst takes lead at 10-under-par in third-round play at LPGA event in Prattville, Ala; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Austin Ernst of the United States took the lead at 10 under par before darkness forced the suspension of third-round play in a weather-delayed L.P.G.A. event in Prattville, Ala.

headline.main: American Leads in Alabama as Sun Sets
